    <a name="FAQ" id="FAQ" class="anchor"></a>
    <h2 class="text-red-dark">FAQ</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-7">
        <h4 class="text-red-light">Is Paton Redevelopment certified as an MWBE firm?</h4>
        <p>No, Paton Redevelopment is not currently certified as a MWBE Developer, however our company has dedicated its efforts and deliverance to contract MWBE certified subcontractors on our projects. In the future, Paton Redevelopment does plan to become MWBE certified.</p>
        <hr class="my-4 col-4">
        <h4 class="text-red-light">Does Paton Redevelopment provide commercial development?</h4>
        <p>Paton Redevelopment is currently concentrated on new residential and renovation of residential homes and buildings. Our company does plan to do commercial projects in the future.</p>
        <hr class="my-4 col-4">
        <h4 class="text-red-light">Does Paton Redevelopment build for customers with their own finance?</h4>
        <p>Yes, from time to time, Paton Redevelopment will build for customers with their own finance for their residence.</p>
